  "english": [
    "<b>he turns it</b> into <b>manure,</b> i.e., the chaff acts like manure, and an excessive amount of manure damages the seeds.",
    "<strong>MISHNA:</strong> <b>One must distance</b> animal <b>carcasses, and graves, and a tannery [<i>haburseki</i>],</b> a place where hides are processed, <b>fifty cubits from the city. One may establish a tannery only on the east side of the city,</b> because winds usually blow from the west and the foul smells would therefore be blown away from the residential area. <b>Rabbi Akiva says: One may establish</b> a tannery <b>on any side</b> of a city <b>except for the west,</b> as the winds blowing from that direction will bring the odors into the city, <b>and one must distance</b> it <b>fifty cubits</b> from the city. <b>One must distance from vegetables water in which flax is steeped,</b> because this water ruins them; <b>and</b> likewise one must distance <b>leeks from onions, and mustard from bees. And Rabbi Yosei permits</b> one not to do so in the case <b>of mustard.</b>",
    "<strong>GEMARA:</strong> <b>A dilemma was raised before</b> the Sages: With regard to <b>what</b> case <b>is Rabbi Akiva speaking?</b> Did he mean that <b>one may establish</b> a tannery <b>on any side</b> of a city, <b>and</b> one may even <b>place</b> the tannery <b>close</b> to the city, <b>except for the west side,</b> where <b>one must establish it at a distance of fifty cubits? Or perhaps</b> he meant that <b>one may establish</b> a tannery <b>on any side and distance it fifty cubits, except for the west side,</b> where one <b>may not establish</b> a tannery <b>at all.</b>",
    "The Gemara cites a proof: <b>Come</b> and <b>hear, as it is taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i>: <b>Rabbi Akiva says</b> that <b>one may establish</b> a tannery <b>on any side</b> of the city <b>and distance it fifty cubits, except for the west side,</b> where one <b>may not establish</b> a tannery <b>at all, because</b> the western wind is <b>frequent.</b>",
    "§ With regard to the last statement of the <i>baraita</i>, <b>Rava said to Rav Naḥman: What</b> does <b>frequent</b> mean in this context? <b>If we say</b> it means <b>frequent among the winds,</b> i.e., this wind blows all the time, that is difficult. <b>But doesn’t Rav Ḥanan bar Abba say</b> that <b>Rav says: Four winds blow every day</b> from different directions, <b>and the northern wind</b> blows <b>with each of</b> the other three; <b>as, if this were not so,</b> i.e., if it did not blow, <b>the world would not exist for even one hour,</b> as the northern wind is pleasant and tempers the bitter effects of the other winds. <b>And the southern wind</b> is <b>harsher than all of them, and were it not</b> for the angel named <b><i>Ben Netz</i>,</b> who <b>stops it</b> from blowing even harder, it would <b>destroy the</b> entire <b>world, as it is stated: “Does the hawk [<i>netz</i>] soar by your wisdom, and stretch her wings toward the south?”</b> (Job 39:26). This indicates that the northern wind is the most constant, not the western wind.",
    "<b>Rather, what</b> is the meaning of <b>frequent?</b> It means <b>frequent with the Divine Presence,</b> i.e., the Divine Presence is found on the western side, and therefore it is inappropriate to set up a tannery there with its foul odors. <b>As Rabbi Yehoshua ben Levi says: Come and let us be grateful to our ancestors who revealed</b> to us <b>the place of prayer, as it is written: “And the hosts of heaven bow down to You”</b> (Nehemiah 9:6). Since the celestial bodies move from east to west, they bow in that direction, which indicates that the Divine Presence is in the west.",
    "<b>Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov objects to this: But perhaps</b> the celestial bodies are <b>like a servant who receives a gift from his master and walks backward</b> while <b>bowing.</b> If so, the Divine Presence is in the east and the celestial bodies are moving backward. The Gemara comments: Indeed, this is <b>difficult,</b> i.e., the verse does not provide a definitive proof.",
    "The Gemara comments: <b>And Rabbi Oshaya holds</b> that <b>the Divine Presence</b> is found <b>in every place, as Rabbi Oshaya says: What</b> is the meaning of that <b>which is written: “You are the Lord, even You alone, You have made heaven…</b>You preserve them all alive and the hosts of heaven bow down to You” (Nehemiah 9:6)? This indicates that <b>Your messengers are not like the messengers of flesh and blood. The messengers of flesh and blood return to the place from where they were sent</b> to report on <b>their mission. But Your messengers return</b> and report on <b>their mission from the</b> very same <b>place</b> to <b>which they are sent, as it is stated “Can you send forth lightnings, that they may go out and say to you: Here we are?”</b> (Job 38:35). The verse <b>does not state: They will come and say,</b> i.e., they do not return to their point of departure, <b>but: “They may go out and say,”</b> which <b>teaches that the Divine Presence</b> is found <b>in every place.</b>",
    "The Gemara comments: <b>And Rabbi Yishmael, too, holds</b> that <b>the Divine Presence</b> is <b>in every place, as</b> one of the Sages of <b>the school of Rabbi Yishmael taught: From where</b> is it derived <b>that the Divine Presence</b> is <b>in every place? As it is stated: “And behold the angel who spoke with me went forth, and another angel went out to meet him”</b> (Zechariah 2:7). Although both angels were coming from the Divine Presence, the verse <b>does not state: After him, but: “To meet him,”</b> which <b>teaches that the Divine Presence</b> is <b>in every place,</b> and therefore the angels depart for their missions from every place.",
    "<b>And Rav Sheshet, too, holds</b> that <b>the Divine Presence</b> is <b>in every place, as Rav Sheshet said to his servant: Set me facing any direction</b> to pray <b>except for the east.</b> Rav Sheshet, who was blind, required the assistance of his aide to prepare for prayer. He explained to his servant: <b>And</b> the reason I do not wish to face east is <b>not because it does not contain the Divine Presence, but because the heretics instruct</b> people to pray <b>in that</b> direction.",
    "<b>But Rabbi Abbahu says: The Divine Presence</b> is <b>in the west, as Rabbi Abbahu says: What</b> is the meaning of <b><i>oriyya</i>,</b> which is a name for the west? It means <b>the air of God [<i>avir Yah</i>],</b> i.e., this is the place of the Divine Presence.",
    "The Gemara cites a statement connected to the four winds. <b>Rav Yehuda said: What</b> is the meaning of that <b>which is written: “My doctrine shall drop as the rain,</b> my speech shall distill as the dew; as the small rain upon the tender growth, and as the showers upon the herb” (Deuteronomy 32:2)? “My doctrine shall drop [<i>ya’arof</i> ] as the rain”; <b>this is the western wind, which comes from the back of [<i>me’orpo</i>] the world,</b> as the west is also referred to as the back.",
    "<b>“My speech shall distill [<i>tizzal</i>] as the dew”; this is the northern wind, which</b> brings dry air that reduces the rain and grain and thereby <b>devalues [<i>mazzelet</i>] gold.</b> When grain crops are reduced their price appreciates, and consequently the value of gold decreases. <b>And in addition, it says: “You who lavish [<i>hazzalim</i>] gold out of the bag”</b> (Isaiah 46:6).",
    "<b>“As the small rain [<i>kisirim</i>] upon the tender growth”; this is the eastern wind that rages through [<i>maseret</i>] the entire world like a demon [<i>sa’ir</i>]</b> when it blows strongly. <b>“And as the showers upon the herb”; this is the southern wind, which raises showers and causes herbs to grow.</b>",
    "<b>It is taught</b> in a <i>baraita</i> that <b>Rabbi Eliezer says:</b> The <b>world</b>"
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>שֶׁעוֹשֶׂה אוֹתוֹ גָּלָל. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>מַתְנִי׳</strong></big> מַרְחִיקִין אֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        0,
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַנְּבֵלוֹת וְאֶת הַקְּבָרוֹת וְאֶת הַבּוּרְסְקִי מִן הָעִיר –",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חֲמִשִּׁים אַמָּה. אֵין עוֹשִׂין בּוּרְסְקִי אֶלָּא לְמִזְרַח",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הָעִיר. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov I, fourth-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"2465\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov I\" data-name-he=\"רבי עקיבא בן יוסף\">רַבִּי עֲקִיבָא</span> אוֹמֵר: לְכׇל רוּחַ הוּא עוֹשֶׂה,",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חוּץ מִמַּעֲ<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rava, first-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"2578\" data-full-name=\"Rava\" data-name-he=\"רב\">רָב</span>ָהּ; וּמַרְחִיק חֲמִשִּׁים אַמָּה.",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וּמֵרְחִיקִין אֶת הַמִּשְׁרָה מִן הַיָּרָק, וְאֶת",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַכְּרֵישִׁין מִן הַבְּצָלִים, וְאֶת הַחַרְדָּל מִן",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַדְּבוֹרִים. <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Ivsi ben Hlfta, fifth-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"1657\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Ivsi ben Hlfta\" data-name-he=\"רבי יוסי בן חלפתא\">וְרַבִּי יוֹסֵי</span> מַתִּיר בְּחַרְדָּל.",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><big><strong>גְּמָ׳</strong></big> אִיבַּעְיָא לְהוּ: <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov I, fourth-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"2465\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov I\" data-name-he=\"רבי עקיבא בן יוסף\">רַבִּי עֲקִיבָא</span> הֵיכִי קָאָמַר? לְכׇל",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "רוּחַ הוּא עוֹשֶׂה וְסוֹמֵךְ, חוּץ מִמַּעֲרָבָהּ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּמַרְחִיק חֲמִשִּׁים אַמָּה וְעוֹשֶׂה; אוֹ דִּלְמָא: לְכׇל רוּחַ",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הוּא עוֹשֶׂה וּמַרְחִיק חֲמִשִּׁים אַמָּה, חוּץ מִמַּעֲרָבָהּ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאֵינוֹ עוֹשֶׂה כְּלָל? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּא שְׁמַע: דְּתַנְיָא, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov I, fourth-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"2465\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov I\" data-name-he=\"רבי עקיבא בן יוסף\">רַבִּי עֲקִיבָא</span>",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹמֵר: לְכׇל רוּחַ הוּא עוֹשֶׂה וּמַרְחִיק חֲמִשִּׁים",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אַמָּה, חוּץ מִמַּעֲרָבָהּ דְּאֵינוֹ עוֹשֶׂה כׇּל עִיקָּר,",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִפְּנֵי שֶׁהִיא תְּדִירָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֲמַר לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav I, fourth-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"2582\" data-full-name=\"Rav I\" data-name-he=\"רבא\">רָבָא</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ḥanan bar Abba, third-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"2285\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ḥanan bar Abba\" data-name-he=\"רב נחמן בר יעקב\">לְרַב נַחְמָן</span>: מַאי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "תְּדִירָא? אִילֵּימָא תְּדִירָא בְּרוּחוֹת, וְהָא אָמַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Ḥanan bar Abba, second-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"1327\" data-full-name=\"Rav Ḥanan bar Abba\" data-name-he=\"רב חנן בר רבא\">רַב חָנָן בַּר אַבָּא</span> אָמַר רַב: אַרְבַּע רוּחוֹת מְנַשְּׁבוֹת",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּכׇל יוֹם, וְרוּחַ צְפוֹנִית עִם כּוּלָּן; שֶׁאִילְמָלֵא כֵּן –",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אֵין הָעוֹלָם מִתְקַיֵּים אֲפִילּוּ שָׁעָה אַחַת. וְרוּחַ",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּרוֹמִית קָשָׁה מִכּוּלָּן, וְאִילְמָלֵא בֶּן נֵץ שֶׁמַּעֲמִידָהּ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַחְרֶבֶת אֶת הָעוֹלָם, שֶׁנֶּאֱמַר:",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״הֲמִבִּינָתְךָ יַאֲבֶר נֵץ, יִפְרֹשׂ כְּנָפָו לְתֵימָן״!",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֶלָּא מַאי תְּדִירָא – תְּדִירָא בִּשְׁכִינָה. דְּאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Levi, first-generation II Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"1544\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Levi\" data-name-he=\"רבי יהושע בן לוי\">רַבִּי יְהוֹשֻׁעַ בֶּן לֵוִי</span>:",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בּוֹאוּ וְנַחֲזִיק טוֹבָה לַאֲבוֹתֵינוּ, שֶׁהוֹדִיעוּ מְקוֹם תְּפִלָּה –",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דִּכְתִיב: ״וּצְבָא הַשָּׁמַיִם לְךָ מִשְׁתַּחֲוִים״.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>מַתְקֵיף לַהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov, third-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"286\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רב אחא בר יעקב\">רַב אַחָא בַּר יַעֲקֹב</span>: וְדִלְמָא כְּעֶבֶד",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁנּוֹטֵל פְּרָס מֵרַבּוֹ, וְחוֹזֵר לַאֲחוֹרָיו וּמִשְׁתַּחֲוֶה!",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "קַשְׁיָא. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Avshaia Rbh I, first-generation II Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"239\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Avshaia Rbh I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אושעיא רבה\">וְרַבִּי אוֹשַׁעְיָא</span> סָבַר: שְׁכִינָה בְּכׇל מָקוֹם.",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rabbi Avshaia Rbh I, first-generation II Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"239\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Avshaia Rbh I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אושעיא רבה\">רַבִּי אוֹשַׁעְיָא</span>, מַאי דִּכְתִיב: ״אַתָּה הוּא",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "ה׳ לְבַדֶּךָ, אַתָּה עָשִׂיתָ אֶת הַשָּׁמַיִם וְגוֹ׳״?",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁלוּחֶיךָ לֹא כִּשְׁלוּחֵי בָּשָׂר וָדָם; שְׁלוּחֵי בָּשָׂר",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וָדָם, מִמָּקוֹם שֶׁמִּשְׁתַּלְּחִים – לְשָׁם מַחֲזִירִים",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁלִיחוּתָן; אֲבָל שְׁלוּחֶיךָ, לְמָקוֹם שֶׁמִּשְׁתַּלְּחִין –",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִשָּׁם מַחְזִירִין שְׁלִיחוּתָן, שֶׁנֶּאֱמַר: ״הַתְשַׁלַּח",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּרָקִים וְיֵלֵכוּ וְיֹאמְרוּ לְךָ הִנֵּנוּ״ – ״יָבוֹאוּ וְיֹאמְרוּ״",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֹא נֶאֱמַר, אֶלָּא ״וְיֵלֵכוּ וְיֹאמְרוּ״, מְלַמֵּד שֶׁהַשְּׁכִינָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּכׇל מָקוֹם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאַף <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Levi II, fourth-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"1979\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Levi II\" data-name-he=\"רבי ישמעאל בן אלישע\">רַבִּי יִשְׁמָעֵאל</span> סָבַר שְׁכִינָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּכׇל מָקוֹם. דְּתָנָא דְּבֵי <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Levi II, fourth-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"1979\" data-full-name=\"Rabbi Yehoshua ben Levi II\" data-name-he=\"רבי ישמעאל בן אלישע\">רַבִּי יִשְׁמָעֵאל</span>: מִנַּיִן",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁשְּׁכִינָה בְּכׇל מָקוֹם? שֶׁנֶּאֱמַר: ״הִנֵּה הַמַּלְאָךְ",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "הַדֹּבֵר בִּי יֹצֵא, וּמַלְאָךְ אַחֵר יֹצֵא לִקְרָאתוֹ״ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "״אַחֲרָיו״ לֹא נֶאֱמַר, אֶלָּא ״לִקְרָאתוֹ״, מְלַמֵּד",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שֶׁשְּׁכִינָה בְּכׇל מָקוֹם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>וְאַף <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Sheshet, third-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"2938\" data-full-name=\"Rav Sheshet\" data-name-he=\"רב ששת\">רַב שֵׁשֶׁת</span> סָבַר",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "שְׁכִינָה בְּכׇל מָקוֹם. דַּאֲמַר לֵיהּ <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Sheshet, third-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"2938\" data-full-name=\"Rav Sheshet\" data-name-he=\"רב ששת\">רַב שֵׁשֶׁת</span> <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Come I, first-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"2924\" data-full-name=\"Come I\" data-name-he=\"שמעיה\">לְשַׁמָּעֵיהּ</span>:",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לְכׇל רוּחָתָא אוֹקְמַן, לְבַר מִמִּזְרָח. וְלָאו מִשּׁוּם",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּלֵית בֵּיהּ שְׁכִינָה, אֶלָּא מִשּׁוּם דְּמוֹרוּ בֵּהּ",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מִינֵי. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"10\" type=\"start\">&star;</span><span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Aḥa I, third-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"92\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אבהו\">וְרַבִּי אֲבָהוּ</span> אָמַר: שְׁכִינָה בַּמַּעֲרָב –",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּאָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Aḥa I, third-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"92\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa I\" data-name-he=\"רבי אבהו\">רַבִּי אֲבָהוּ</span>: מַאי ״אוֹרְיָה״? אֲוִיר יָהּ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"11\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-amora\" data-sage-type=\"amora\" title=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov, second-generation Amora.\" data-authority-id=\"1394\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רב יהודה בר יחזקאל\">רַב יְהוּדָה</span>,",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַאי דִּכְתִיב ״יַעֲרֹף כַּמָּטָר לִקְחִי״? זוֹ רוּחַ",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "מַעֲרָבִית, שֶׁבָּאָה מֵעׇרְפּוֹ שֶׁל עוֹלָם. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"12\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>״תִּזַּל כַּטַּל אִמְרָתִי״ – זוֹ רוּחַ צְפוֹנִית,",
      "segment_ids": [
        12
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "שֶׁמַּזֶּלֶת אֶת הַזָּהָב. וְכֵן הוּא אוֹמֵר: ״הַזָּלִים זָהָב מִכִּיס״. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"13\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>״כִּשְׂעִירִם עֲלֵי דֶשֶׁא״ –",
      "segment_ids": [
        13
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "זוֹ רוּחַ מִזְרָחִית, שֶׁמַּסְעֶרֶת אֶת כׇּל הָעוֹלָם כְּשָׂעִיר. ״וְכִרְבִיבִים עֲלֵי עֵשֶׂב״ – זוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        13
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "655px",
      "text": "רוּחַ דְּרוֹמִית, שֶׁהִיא מַעֲלָה רְבִיבִים וּמְגַדֶּלֶת עֲשָׂבִים. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"14\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תַּנְיָא, <span class=\"name-reference-marker name-reference-tanna\" data-sage-type=\"tanna\" title=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov, third-generation Tanna.\" data-authority-id=\"417\" data-full-name=\"Rav Aḥa bar Ya’akov\" data-name-he=\"רבי אליעזר בן הורקנוס\">רַבִּי אֱלִיעֶזֶר</span> אוֹמֵר: עוֹלָם",
      "segment_ids": [
        14
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>שעושה</b> <b>אותו</b> <b>גלל.</b> מרבה לו זבל ושורף את הזרעים שנזרעו בו:"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>מתני'</b> <b>את</b> <b>הנבלות</b> <b>ואת</b> <b>הקברות</b> <b>כו'.</b> משום ריח רע: <b>אלא</b> <b>למזרח</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>העיר.</b> שאין הרוח מזרחית קשה תדיר אא\"כ באה לפורענות"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אבל כדרכה היא חמה ומנשבת בנחת דכתיב (<a href=\"https://www.sefaria.org/Jonah.4.8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-sefaria-ref=\"Jonah.4.8\">יונה ד׳:ח׳</a>) רוח קדים"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חרישית ותך השמש וגו' לפיכך אינה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מביאה הרוח לעיר: <b>חוץ</b> <b>מן</b> <b>מערבה.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בגמ' מפרש טעמא: <b>גמ'</b> <b>וסומך.</b> אינו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "צריך להרחיק נ' אמה: <b>שאינו</b> <b>עושה</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>כלל.</b> ומרחיק נ' אמה דקאמר ר\"ע"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אשאר רוחות דרישא קאי: <b>תדירא</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>ברוחות.</b> אותו צד תדיר ברוח"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שרוח מערבית מנשבת תדיר משאר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רוחות: <b>רוח</b> <b>צפונית</b> <b>מנשבת</b> <b>עם</b> <b>כל</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אחת.</b> מהרוחות לפי שהיא רכה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ומתוקה וצלולה כדאמר ביבמות"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "(<a href=\"/bava_batra/72a\">דף עב.</a>) וממתקתן: <b>בן</b> <b>נץ.</b> מלאך"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "העשוי בדמות נץ: <b>מעמידה.</b> בכנפיו:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>תדירא</b> <b>בשכינה.</b> במערב היא שוכנת:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לאבותינו.</b> אנשי כנה\"ג שאמרו מקרא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "זה בספר עזרא: <b>וצבא</b> <b>השמים.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "השמש והירח העומדים במזרח: <b>לך</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>משתחוים.</b> למערב: <b>ודלמא.</b> הם"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למזרח משתחוים וכי תימא אין דרך"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להשתחוות סמוך לרב הם עושין"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כעבד שנטל פרס מרבו וחוזר לאחוריו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ומשתחוה כשהוא הולך לאחוריו משנטל"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "פרס מתרחק תמיד בהשתחויה:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>פרס.</b> מתן: <b>אתה</b> <b>הוא</b> <b>ה'</b> <b>לבדך.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בתר וצבא השמים כתיב ועל עסקי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שליחות צבא השמים הוא משבח"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואומר אתה הוא לבדך במדה זו:"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>לשם</b> <b>מחזירין</b> <b>שליחותן.</b> כשבאין לומר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עשינו שליחותך צריכין לשוב אל מקום"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שהשולחם עומד שם: <b>למקום</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>שמשתלחין.</b> פי' באותו מקום שנשתלחו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שם אף שם השכינה מצויה ואומרים לו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עשינו שליחותך: <b>והנה</b> <b>המלאך</b> <b>הדובר</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>בי</b> <b>יוצא.</b> בנבואת זכריה למוד את"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ירושלים כמה ארכה וגו' ומלאך אחר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "יוצא לסתור שליחותו של ראשון שחזר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בו המקום ולא יתן בה מדה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואומר פרזות תשב ירושלים והרי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שניהם מאת השכינה באים ואחריו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לא נאמר אלא לקראתו זה בא מכאן"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "וזה בא מכאן: <b>רב</b> <b>ששת.</b> מאור עינים"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוה: <b>לכל</b> <b>רוחתא</b> <b>אוקמן.</b> העמידני"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "להתפלל: <b>דמורו</b> <b>בה</b> <b>מיני.</b> תלמידי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עובדי ע\"ז מורים הוראה להתפלל"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "במזרח: <b>אוריה.</b> אני שמעתי כך קורין"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למערב בלשון פרסי. ול\"נ שכך קורין"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "למזרח בלשון לעז והיינו דקאמר אויר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "יה שהשכינה במערב ופניו למזרח"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נמצא המזרח אוירו: <b>יערוף</b> <b>כמטר</b> <b>לקחי.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משה רבינו דימה את התורה לארבע"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "רוחות כשם שאי אפשר בלא הם כך"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אי אפשר לעולם בלא תורה: <b>מערפו</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>של</b> <b>עולם.</b> אני שמעתי מחזקו של עולם"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "על שם שהשכינה במערב ס\"ל ואני"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אומר מאחוריו של עולם שהמערב קרוי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "אחור שנאמר הן קדם אהלך ואיננו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואחור ולא אבין וגו' (<a href=\"https://www.sefaria.org/Job.23.8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-sefaria-ref=\"Job.23.8\">איוב כ״ג:ח׳</a>): <b>שמזלת</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>את</b> <b>הזהב.</b> שמחממת ומביאה שרב"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ורעבון בא והזהב זל: <b>וכן</b> <b>הוא</b> <b>אומר.</b>"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דכתיב זילותא גבי זהב: <b>כשעיר.</b> שד:"
    }
  ],
  "tosafot": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>שעושה אותו גלל</b></big>. אע\"ג דגלל משביח הקרקע כשהיא כולה"
    },
    {
      "width": "390px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "גלל מזיק. <big><b>אין עושין בורסקי אלא למזרח העיר</b></big>."
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "משום דרוח מערבי שהוא קשה ירחיק ויוליך הריח מן העיר כדאמרי'"
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "(<a href=\"/berakhot/40a\">ברכות מ.</a>) הישן למזרח גרנו דמו בראשו מפני שרוח מערבית מביא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הקש בחוטמו. <big><b>מפני שהיא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תדירה</b></big>. לא גרסי' מ\"ט דמן הברייתא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "היא דהכי איתא בתוספתא (פ\"א ע\"ש)."
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>וצבא השמים לך משתחוים</b></big>. וא\"ת"
    },
    {
      "width": "200px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בלילה נמי במזרח משתחוים"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וי\"ל דאין לנו ללמוד אלא ממה שאנו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "רואין וא\"ת ואמאי לא נדע מקום"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תפלה מבית המקדש שהיתה שם"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שכינה במערב וי\"ל דמשם אין ללמוד"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דאע\"ג דשכינה בכל מקום אי אפשר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "להשים ארון וכפורת אלא בצד אחד"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "וריצב\"א אומר דמשם אין ללמוד"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דשכינה במערב דנהי דבית קדשי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הקדשים היה במערב המקדש מ\"מ"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הארון שהשכינה שם כדכתיב (שמות כה)"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ונועדתי לך שם היה במזרח בית קדשי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הקדשים. <big><b>לכל רוחתא אוקמן</b></big>."
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כל הני אמוראי לית להו הא דתניא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בברכות (<a href=\"/berakhot/30a\">דף ל.</a>) שחייב אדם להתפלל"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "נגד ירושלים משום דכתיב והתפללו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אליך דרך ארצם אלא סברי כר'"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ישמעאל דאמר בכ\"מ שכינה ומאן"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דאמר שכינה במערב סבר כר\"ע"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דאמר מפני שהיא תדירה ור' חנינא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דשמעתין דאמר כגון אתון דיתבון"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לצפונא דארעא דישראל אדרימו סבר"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לה כברייתא דברכות."
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>אוריה</b></big>. לשון שפ\"ה דאוריה מערב"
    },
    {
      "width": "180px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "נראה לר\"ת ולר\"ח עיקר."
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>רוח מערבית שבא מערפו של"
    },
    {
      "width": "210px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "עולם</b></big>. כדפי' בקונט' מאחורו"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "של עולם דמערב קרוי אחור דכתיב"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אחור וקדם צרתני ודרשינן [בחגיגה]"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "(<a href=\"/bava_batra/12a\">דף יב.</a>) לענין מזרח ומערב וכתיב"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "נמי ארם מקדם ופלשתים מאחור"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "(ישעיה ט) וקרי נמי דרום ימין ולצפון"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שמאל כדאמרי' בשמעתין והיינו משום"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דשכינה במערב ופני השכינה למזרח"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לכך קרוי מערב אחור ומזרח קדם"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ודרום ימין וצפון שמאל ולמ\"ד שכינה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בכל מקום צ\"ל דהאי דקרי מזרח"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "קדם ומערב אחור ודרום ימין וצפון"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שמאל משום שכינה בבית המקדש"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שהיה במערב ופני השכינה כלפי"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ישראל שהיו במזרח ומשתחוים שם."
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>הגה\"ה</b></big>. ורבינו יצחק בר יהודה"
    },
    {
      "width": "190px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "פירש דכשעמד אדם הראשון"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כשנברא היו פניו למזרח ואין נראה"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שהיה ערפו כלפי השכינה למאן"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דאמר שכינה במערב, ע\"כ הגה\"ה."
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>רוח מזרחית שמסערת כל העולם"
    },
    {
      "width": "210px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כולו</b></big>. והא דמשמע במתניתין"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שהיא נוחה מכל הרוחות היינו כשהיא"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "באה כדרכה אבל כשבאה לפורענות"
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "היא מסערת כדפי' הקונט' במתניתין."
    }
  ]
}